data.description: Wow, this 5 bedroom, 3 bath home has it all. Open living area, center wall fireplace, kitchen island/snack bar and utility room. Hardwood flooring throughout the foyer, great room, kitchen and dining room. The master bath is awesome with its walk-through shower, large tub, double vanities, linen closet, big walk-in closet and a private toilet. Upstairs is a 4th bedroom, full bath and finished bonus room that can serve as the 5th bedroom. Double garage with storage area, large covered patio, gutters, fully sodded yard and landscaping. CAN CLOSE IN 30 DAYS!
